{"tid":1945626,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔兔獨特的視覺 !","createTime":"2020-03-27T07:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T19:38:40.000Z","uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0beb2094ea8eefb641bbb97173faefc5c4b7a9b6","tid":1945626,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:45:29.000Z","msg":"兔子大眼睛和大耳朵的構造令牠們在大自然內容易偵測到被補獵者追食。因為眼睛範圍大，<span style=\"color: gold;\">你在牠後面也會看到你</span>。<span style=\"color: gold;\">側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</span>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度 (所以有時食物在牠下巴下面看不到)。&nbsp;兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以牠們不是無視你，你一直是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_bDc0r8YA80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_bDc0r8YA80&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNvpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=dc02e7de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_bDc0r8YA80</a>"},{"pid":"249ce0f4c99be79761e90757d3ce764ae9184251","tid":1945626,"uid":32263,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"兔兔巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7255f0a603d5da40d1fefb7ef9ae36bd60b466","tid":1945626,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"249ce0f4c99be79761e90757d3ce764ae9184251","tid":1945626,"uid":32263,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"兔兔巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"ha<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23402566c8675eca3d681cb7271bdeee2eb6918f","tid":1945626,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4d1a1b5e2a72e1573fa8dedca2b10780b208b1","tid":1945626,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3e60e553da4d915e983ad6a38d0d8aa318e952","tid":1945626,"uid":100016,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"屌你仲未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f0bb465eb79b8d39d5540e91f000084da4971e","tid":1945626,"uid":71393,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kn10Jf1x24Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKn10Jf1x24Q&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNvpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=7dc11c01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kn10Jf1x24Q</a><br />\n佢地係咪識嬲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42c92e31f1c1537bb746cb35552a6e26dc42d96","tid":1945626,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed890038b9f084fa9c5e40ee4ddd800d410df52","tid":1945626,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子是應該要被絕育...(寵物兔)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"be2e2365464809440437906b348ab895c902b2ca","tid":1945626,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"In Tokyo, it's been raining on and off all day. In Osaka, it's just spitting a little. In Fukuoka, it's spitting too. In Kyoto, it's pouring. In Hiroshima, it is pouring rain outside. In Nagasaki, it's really coming down out there."},{"pid":"85d719968b426cc8162532655963bc9c522692ee","tid":1945626,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c1554187c52580132fa6977b66b92e09e6cf2b","tid":1945626,"uid":212274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"樓主記唔記得我，係你fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0688d18c9911dd0e17e0ce3e1375d6bbf5f6d8","tid":1945626,"uid":246500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T19:38:40.000Z","msg":"btw 樓主最鍾意prokofiev邊隻作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}